						ut scias non otiose <lb/> id posuisse utrumque.</p>
					<p>18. <hi rend="italic">[Alias cap.</hi> III.] Diximus quid scriptum sit, col- <milestone unit="PLSection" n="A"/><lb/> ligamus sententiam : <hi rend="italic">Omnis,</hi>
