							<lb/> profanaverint , et mandata mea non custodierint;<lb/> visitabe</hi> in <hi rend="italic">virga iniquitates</hi> eorum, <hi rend="italic">et</hi> in <hi rend="italic">flagellis delicta<lb/> eorum : misericordiam autem meam</hi> non <hi rend="italic">disperdam ab<lb/> eia (Psal.</hi> LXXXVIII, 32, 33). Omnibus igitur
