						<hi rend="italic">Potum dabis eis in lacrymis</hi> in <hi rend="italic">mensura
							(Psal.</hi> LXVIX , <lb/> 6); ut ipsa mœstitia e mensaram habeat, ne forte <lb/>
						abundatiore tristitiia bsorbeatur (II <hi rend="italic">Cor.</hi> II, <hi rend="italic">5 et seq.),</hi>
						<lb/> qui agit pœnitentiam, sicut scripsit ad Corinthios : <lb/>
						<hi rend="italic">Quid vultis ? In virga veniam ad vos,</hi> an <hi rend="italic">in
							charitate,<lb/> spirituque mansuetudinis</hi>( I <hi rend="italic">Cor.</hi> IV, 21) ?
