							cuties eum virga, animam aulem ejus a morte liberabis</hi>
						<lb/> ( <hi rend="italic">Prov.</hi> XXIII, 14 ).</p>
					<p>60. Quid esset in virga venire , docet invectio for­ <lb/> nicationis , accusatio
